                  <p lang="EN-US" paraeid="{5ea8eacb-14f4-4815-b648-1629639bf37d}{170}" paraid="1940615573" xml:lang="EN-US">Biases and Inequality have been around since aeons. Countries and institutes around the globe, have actively been concerned about bringing a change to it when it comes to racial, gender and economic inequalities. Institutions can take affirmative actions to reduce the effects of inequality in their countries, through the means of recruiting members of different groups or having special quotas.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                  <p lang="EN-US" paraeid="{5ea8eacb-14f4-4815-b648-1629639bf37d}{178}" paraid="153718033" xml:lang="EN-US">Gender inequalities are experienced differently around the globe. It's based on biological and psychological aspects.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                  <p lang="EN-US" paraeid="{5ea8eacb-14f4-4815-b648-1629639bf37d}{186}" paraid="744673904" xml:lang="EN-US">Economic inequalities have different dimensions like distribution of income, wealth, consumption power etc.&nbsp;</p>
